<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-11-14T17:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-11-14T17:00:00-05:00" n="355" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d355">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">865.01/1: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Italy</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_PTN1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Page</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Rome</hi>
                                </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-11-14T23:00:00+01:00">November 14, 1918—11
                                    p.m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received November 15—12:21 p.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>2353. Learn that Italy has in contemplation creation of 5 new provinces,
                            Dalmatia, Trieste, Trentino, Gorizia, Bolzano. They may have already
                            matured plans.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="#p_PTN1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Nelson Page</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>